gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 113, Rockets 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Rockets, 113-106. Naz Reid led the way for the Timberwolves with 25 points and six rebounds, while Anthony Edwards added 21 points and five rebounds in the victory. Jalen Green (26 points, five rebounds, six assists) and Fred VanVleet (22 points, five rebounds, five assists, five steals) combined for 48 points for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 52-23 on the season, while the Rockets fall to 38-37.
